了笔者自身的一些理解..如有不对欢迎指正…</p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n  <!-- 音乐外链-->\n  <iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"330\" height=\"86\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=454224842&auto=0&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3 id=\"hexo-g-hexo-generate\"><a href=\"#hexo-g-hexo-generate\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo g  || hexo generate..\"></a>hexo g  || hexo generate..</h3><p>该命令执行后在hexo站点根目录下生成public文件夹…</p>\n<hr>\n\n<h3 id=\"hexo-d\"><a href=\"#hexo-d\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo d\"></a>hexo d</h3><p>通过public文件夹在本地生成.deploy_git文件夹…<br>并将编译后的文件上传至 GitHub…<br>通常在上文中的<strong>hexo g</strong>后使用…</p>\n<hr>\n\n<h3 id=\"hexo-clean\"><a href=\"#hexo-clean\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo clean\"></a>hexo clean</h3><p>把上文中的生成public文件夹删除…<br>也就是俗称的清除缓存…<br>在特定的条件下会使用…</p>\n<hr>\n\n<h3 id=\"hexo-s-hexo-server\"><a href=\"#hexo-s-hexo-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo s  || hexo server\"></a>hexo s  || hexo server</h3><p>启动本地hexo服务器…<br>一般默认地址为:</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"r